lead_paragraph: As much as Ed Orgeron might have preferred a different route to the top coaching job at LSU, the Louisiana native was never going to be able to hide his enthusiasm for his new opportunity — and didn't try.

headline.print_headline: Orgeron: Coaching LSU 'a Dream,' Offense Will Be 'Tweaked'
headline.main: Orgeron: Coaching LSU 'a Dream,' Offense Will Be 'Tweaked'
